data.description: This fabulous MainVue resale in Tehaleh is a great big WOW! With sleek and modern architecture and amenities, this greenbelt home is a buyer's turnkey dream! From the sophisticated primary retreat on main with new white wooden custom closets, the culinary dream kitchen; great room concept layout with additional living areas up and down; three car garage and three additional bedrooms up; along with an inviting  indoor/outdoor flow, there are too many features to list! Do see the two gas fireplaces, low maintenance yard, wet bar & pantry, laundry room and storage spaces. Thoughtfully designed and well cared for!
